{%- comment -%}
  Vertex Buy-it-again — "Time to restock" slot for logged-in returning customers.

  Reads `customer.metafields.vertex.repurchase_handles` (JSON array of product
  handles, top-N by Vertex predict score, written by the hairmnl-vertex
  precompute Cloud Function — NOT YET SCHEDULED as of 2026-07; this slot is
  dormant until the job runs).

  J31 rewrite (bd 2i8b.95, phase4 closeout audit): the original bespoke
  .vertex-buy-it-again__* cards bypassed vertex-rec-card (so none of the
  J25–J29 rail styling applied) and filtered only on p.available — missing the
  freebie/salon/exclude-list/in-cart guards the flagship rail carries, on the
  surface MOST likely to contain freebies (purchase history). Now renders the
  shared guard (snippets/vertex-rec-skip.liquid) + the unified card
  (vertex-rec-card) inside standard .vrec-slot rail markup, so all rail
  styling, badges and Quick Buy behavior apply automatically.

  Renders nothing when: anonymous customer, metafield missing/empty, or every
  candidate is skipped by the guard.

  Usage in a parent template/section:
    {% if customer %}
      {% render 'vertex-buy-it-again',
          title: 'Time to restock',
          subtitle: 'Based on your purchase history' %}
    {% endif %}
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if customer -%}
  {%- assign bia_handles = customer.metafields.vertex.repurchase_handles.value -%}
  {%- if bia_handles and bia_handles.size > 0 -%}

    {%- capture bia_rail -%}
      {%- for bia_handle in bia_handles limit: 8 -%}
        {%- assign bia_p = all_products[bia_handle] -%}
        {%- if bia_p and bia_p.handle != blank -%}
          {%- capture bia_skip -%}{%- render 'vertex-rec-skip', product: bia_p, cart: cart -%}{%- endcapture -%}
          {%- unless bia_skip contains 'skip' -%}
            {%- render 'vertex-rec-card', product: bia_p, placement: 'buy_it_again' -%}
          {%- endunless -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endcapture -%}

    {%- assign bia_trimmed = bia_rail | strip -%}
    {%- if bia_trimmed != '' -%}
      <section
        class="vrec-slot vrec-slot--buy_it_again"
        data-vertex-placement="buy_it_again"
        aria-labelledby="vrec-title-buy_it_again"
      >
        <header class="vrec-slot__header">
          <h2 id="vrec-title-buy_it_again"
              class="h2--body section-header__title vrec-slot__title">{{ title | default: 'Time to restock' }}</h2>
          <p class="vrec-slot__subtitle">{{ subtitle | default: 'Based on your purchase history' }}</p>
        </header>
        <div class="vrec-slot__nav-wrap">
          <div class="vrec-slot__rail" role="list">
            {{ bia_rail }}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    {%- endif -%}

  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
